      .container
        .section-item.section-item-1
          img(src='images/edyn_web_diamond.png', alt='', title='')
          h3 Keep tabs on your garden with the Edyn Garden Sensor
          p
            | Conditions in your garden are constantly changing. Know what&rsquo;s happening in real time so you can keep your plants healthy. The Edyn Garden Sensor tracks light, humidity, temperature, soil nutrition, and moisture &mdash; and then cross-references this information with plant databases, soil science, and the weather to give you customized gardening guidance.
        .section-item.section-item-2
          h3 Know what&rsquo;s happening beneath the soil
          p
            | Too often, problems in your garden aren&rsquo;t visible until it&rsquo;s too late. Edyn lets you know what&rsquo;s happening beneath the surface by monitoring minute changes in soil nutrition and moisture &mdash; so you can anticipate and resolve problems before they happen.
          a.button.button-alternate(href='http://www.homedepot.com/p/Edyn-Garden-Sensor-EDYN-001/205833447', target='_blank') Buy Now
    section.section-app.section-dark
      .container
        .carousel
          .carousel-item.carousel-item-1
            img(src='images/edyn_web_hero_phone_dash.jpg', alt='', title='')
            .carousel-content
              h3 Edyn takes the guesswork out of gardening
              p
                | Know exactly what&rsquo;s happening in your garden at a glance. The Edyn app regularly pulls data from your Garden Sensor to give you a snapshot of current conditions in your garden. Stay up to date on the water needs, soil nutrition, and changes in weather that could impact your garden.
          .carousel-item.carousel-item-2
            img(src='images/edyn_web_hero_phone_data.jpg', alt='', title='')
            .carousel-content
              h3 Get tailored guidance based on your garden&rsquo;s conditions
              p
                | Edyn&rsquo;s advice is based on science and data from your garden, not generalities. Know when your plants aren&rsquo;t getting what they need and get recommendations on how to adjust. Dig into the details to see historical trends like how much sunlight you&rsquo;ve had in the past or how cold it was last winter.
          .carousel-item.carousel-item-3
            img(src='images/edyn_web_hero_phone_plantcard.jpg', alt='', title='')
            .carousel-content
              h3 Know what will grow best based on your garden&rsquo;s unique conditions
              p
                | Have Edyn analyze your garden to discover which plants best match its conditions and climate. Edyn&rsquo;s database of over 5,000 plant varieties will provide tips to help you prep your garden and find the optimal spot for any plant.
          .carousel-item.carousel-item-4
            img(src='images/edyn_web_hero_phone_garden.jpg', alt='', title='')
            .carousel-content
              h3 Add plants and watch your garden grow
              p
                | Track your plants&rsquo; growth over time. View all the plants in your garden with quick tips and reminders. Get tailored suggestions based on their growth stage and receive notifications for individual plants that need attention.
          .carousel-item.carousel-item-5
            img(src='images/edyn_web_hero_phone_discovery.jpg', alt='', title='')
            .carousel-content
              h3 Discover plants that grow better together
              p
                | Starting a new garden or wondering what to grow next to your tomatoes? Get inspired with Edyn&rsquo;s curated garden collections. Find plants that grow great together, discourage pests, or make a delicious meal.
          .carousel-item.carousel-item-6
            img(src='images/edyn_web_hero_phone_timeline.jpg', alt='', title='')
            .carousel-content
              h3 Know how to care for your plants at each stage of their life
              p
                | Never wonder what you should do next to help your garden thrive. Learn from the past by easily scrolling through a timeline of activities and milestones, and plan for the future with Edyn&rsquo;s personalized gardening &ldquo;to-dos.&rdquo;
    section.section-valve.section-dark
